    "text": [
        "Dear Mr. Smith,",
        "I am writing to withdraw my admission from your part-time evening course which you recently started on the topic of financial planning.",
        "My name is Tom Hardy and I work as a sales manager. Recently, around 10 days back, I enrolled for your financial planning course, and I particularly opted for your institute because, here, it is being offered as part-time evening course.",
        "Although I have attended it for around 7 days, now I am finding it very difficult to continue it along with my job. I work full-time with Walmart and most of the time it requires to stay back till late. That is why I was not able to attend the class for last 3 days.",
        "Due to above mentioned situation, it will be really difficult for me to continue, so I want to request you to refund my fees paid for this course. I understand that it will be a loss for you, so in order to compensate that you may deduct the amount for the 10 days on pro-rata basis.",
        "I hope you will consider my case favourably.",
        "Yours sincerely,",
        "Tom Hardy"
